{"tid":1700614,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"凌晨閉門失火 100毛主播慘死 父母吸濃煙送院","createTime":"2019-11-08T15:10:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T15:10:49.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"758f0f8c27a336a747b7306311d7f72343839c1f","tid":1700614,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T15:10:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191108/QIX4A3FVW75Y4YVUJN2L45OMCM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191108%2FQIX4A3FVW75Y4YVUJN2L45OMCM%2F&d=zUJDlVqOtbKZlRnsKtUQBIkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=af57e9bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191108%2FQIX4A3FVW75Y4YVUJN2L45OMCM%2F&h=d0ec7480\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191108/QIX4A3FVW75Y4YVUJN2L45OMCM/</a><br />\n<br />\n凌晨閉門失火 100毛主播慘死<br />\n父母吸濃煙送院<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】沙田豐盛苑富盛閣昨凌晨發生一死兩傷奪命火，26歲女死者為網媒《100毛》及《毛記電視》女主播「銀紙彤」，她睡夢中被濃煙嗆醒發現客廳起火，立即喚醒父母逃生，其母親逃出屋外呼救，她與父親疑被煙火阻擋，只好各自退入自己房間待救，其母親與鄰居企圖拉消防喉救火發現無水，消防員趕至開喉救火及救出父親，她則慘被燒死。沙田警區重案組已接手調查此案。<br />\n<br />\n記者：潘志能 鄭文輝 劉柏麟<br />\n<br />\n女死者曾穎欣（英文名Mary）2015年加入《100毛》，兩年後離職，早前重回《100毛》擔任女主播，取名「銀紙彤」，銀紙彤在《毛記電視》主持《膠易現場》，以急口令式報道「財經新聞」。火警中，曾女父親（60歲）及陳姓母親（55歲）吸入濃煙不適及右手受傷，事後送院治療。調查人員在火場未有發現助燃物品，涉事家庭亦無與人結怨，相信火警並無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n《100毛》昨晚稱，得悉Mary離世，同事都感到非常難過，指Mary盡責勤奮、正直善良，她的一切，將長留心中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/iJjXi7kiOZSI_lVH8ZEpzX6c0fE=/802x802/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/QQTZJVZ53M5AZBRTCF3YHM3EQY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FiJjXi7kiOZSI_lVH8ZEpzX6c0fE%3D%2F802x802%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FQQTZJVZ53M5AZBRTCF3YHM3EQY.gif&h=bf3ca3e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n26歲女死者曾穎欣為《100毛》及《毛記電視》女主播「銀紙彤」。<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/WccauZmU3X72jQmuCGTNvpZgyYE=/802x531/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/SLYS4L52V2ZT66LUHD3HMVOTCI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FWccauZmU3X72jQmuCGTNvpZgyYE%3D%2F802x531%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FSLYS4L52V2ZT66LUHD3HMVOTCI.jpg&h=c811e829&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n起火單位火勢猛烈，並迅即波及樓上單位。<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/D3fOzDJ0sJVxAAV-ovbkBao-XsI=/802x447/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/YAPS2C6SOX7UOBJMXGSOOOVDYQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FD3fOzDJ0sJVxAAV-ovbkBao-XsI%3D%2F802x447%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FYAPS2C6SOX7UOBJMXGSOOOVDYQ.jpg&h=cebf3b03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n起火單位女戶主不適送院治理。潘志能攝<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/kfI6qfy5Nj4z57FJS5uV6QBGJJY=/802x531/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/RMCGF62B6RLFZLDGMWCSNGQY2E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FkfI6qfy5Nj4z57FJS5uV6QBGJJY%3D%2F802x531%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FRMCGF62B6RLFZLDGMWCSNGQY2E.jpg&h=7147227c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n火警單位男戶主吸入濃煙不適送院。鄭文輝攝<br />\nAppleDaily<br />\n鄰居戴豬嘴逃生<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：消防喉無水 住客轟管理差<br />\n<br />\n現場為富盛閣9樓一個單位，面積5米乘6米，一廳兩房。據鄰居稱，起火單位原住有曾氏一家四口，年前長女結婚搬出，剩幼女與兩老同住，一家人健談爽朗，平日碰頭都會打招呼。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，曾女與母親住在近門口的房間，父親則住在近窗口房間。昨凌晨1時許，曾女在客廳與父親談天後各自回房休息，至昨凌晨4時許，曾女在房間被濃煙嗆醒，走出查看發現客廳起火，慌忙喚醒父母，其母親隨即逃出屋外連呼「救命」求援，其間疑火勢迅速蔓延，烈燄濃煙擋住門口，曾女與父親未能逃出屋外，只好各自退回房間暫避，街坊發現火警報警，並企圖拉消防喉救火，卻發現消防喉無水。<br />\n<br />\n據同層姓謝男戶主稱，聽到有人高呼「救命」開門查看，發現曾家起火，曾太逃出在家門前呼救，他一度欲拉喉救火，但不懂開啟，他見曾太情緒激動，曾欲帶同她一起逃生，惟曾太疑因女兒被困火場拒絕離開，「我拉佢叫佢走呀，佢仲想衝入屋唔肯走」，後來因太大煙，謝戴着「豬嘴」逃落樓。<br />\n<br />\n消防員到場，全屋已陷於火海，消防開喉撲救，並在火場一房間救出曾父，當時他仍然清醒，火警於半小時後被救熄，消防員在曾女的房間發現她被燒死在地上，房門被焚毀。由於火勢猛烈，大火更波及樓上兩層的單位，其中一單位露台及房間更被焚毀。"}]}